Available Tools: create_report | get_report | list_reports | schedule_report | export_report
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "report_id": "string", "name": "string", "metrics": ["string"], "dimensions": ["string"], "from_date": "string", "to_date": "string" }
Response Schema: { "report_id": "string", "name": "string", "rows": [{}], "total_rows": number, "generated_at": "string" }
---
Question: Schedule a daily email report for yesterday's sales performance by region.
Call: { "func_call": "schedule_report", "report_id": "rpt_daily_sales_001", "name": "Daily Sales by Region", "metrics": ["total_revenue", "units_sold"], "dimensions": ["region", "date"], "from_date": "2023-10-01", "to_date": "2023-10-01" }
Response: { "report_id": "rpt_daily_sales_001", "name": "Daily Sales by Region", "rows": [], "total_rows": 0, "generated_at": "2023-10-02T08:00:00Z" }

